flowchart LR
    User[Human user]
    UI[Streamlit app\n(app.py)]
    KB[Pet care knowledge base]
    Retriever[Retriever / RAG layer]
    Agent[Agentic decision layer]
    Models[Owner / Pet / Task models\n(pawpal_system.py)]
    Scheduler[Scheduler]
    Output[Plan, explanations,\nconflict warnings]
    Tester[pytest suite\n(tests/test_pawpal.py)]
    Reviewer[Human review]

    User --> UI
    UI --> Retriever
    Retriever --> KB
    Retriever --> Agent
    Agent --> Models
    Models --> Scheduler
    Scheduler --> Output
    Output --> User

    Output --> Reviewer
    Tester --> Models
    Tester --> Scheduler
    Tester --> Output

    Agent -. urgent medication / escalation .-> Output
    Agent -. prioritize tasks .-> Scheduler
    Reviewer -. confirms / adjusts .-> UI
